sentences: Lee Joo-myung (Korean: 이주명; born December 1, 1993) is a South Korean actress and model.

She debuted in the television and film industry through the television series My Fellow Citizens! (2019) and is best known for her roles in the television series Missing: The Other Side (2020) and Kairos (2020).
